00:45:55,290 --> 00:45:57,850
<i>Yes, Director.</i>

554
00:45:57,850 --> 00:46:01,720
<i>Yes, I am almost there. Yes.</i>

555
00:46:10,330 --> 00:46:14,600
<i>I think Min Hyeok has gone to see that woman.</i>

556
00:46:14,600 --> 00:46:19,180
<i>No matter what, bring me that child.</i>

