00:55:06,540 --> 00:55:11,680
- Hey, Unni, Unni!
- Hospital, hospital, hospital, go to the hospital!

631
00:55:11,690 --> 00:55:16,830
Get in first, get in. Okay, okay, it's okay.

632
00:55:16,830 --> 00:55:20,810
Unni, I'll wrap things up here and go. 
